#\#CIF_2.0
# Tests: powder diffractogram structured table routing with a small dataset.
# _pd_data.point_id is the PD_DATA parent-category key; _pd_meas.2theta_scan and
# _pd_meas.intensity_total are routed to the pd_meas table. _pd_diffractogram.id
# provides the diffractogram_id context for the FK. _pd_data.point_id provides the
# value for _pd_meas.point_id
# Dictionary: cif_pow

data_test_small_pd_meas
_diffrn_radiation.id    lab_tube
_diffrn_radiation.probe x-ray
_pd_diffractogram.id    test_scan
loop_
  _pd_data.point_id
  _pd_meas.2theta_scan
  _pd_meas.intensity_total
  0  10.000  100.0
  1  10.100  120.0
  2  10.200  110.0
  3  10.300   95.0
  4  10.400  105.0
